item.title: Baba, My Love
item.description: Happy birthday to my dearest Baba, the ultimate Love of my Life. Here is a simple gift box made especially for YOU. My wish on Your birthday is for everyone in this world to have sparkling and glittering hearts filled with Love, helping and uplifting one another. Samastha Lokah Sukhino Bavanthu. I will make You proud. Thank you for everythingâ€¦You are the BEST! Love Always… Your Child, Shivendraa Gallery
